{"tid":1505231,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"屌，其實警察任得d示威者佔領一個區又有咩所謂","createTime":"2019-08-25T13:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T00:38:09.000Z","uid":74778,"like":155,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"46bb1447dbb10ea131f29125aa997ce733d01ca0","tid":1505231,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:17:56.000Z","msg":"下下出力打示威者又比示威者打到摷，有乜為<br />\n<br />\n明知自己係磨心，對面個矛頭又唔係自己，絕大部分政府部門都同林鄭班底劃清界線嘅時候，自己竟然要出全力去保護個政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你咪當到到都係71個立法會咁囉，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VP5CsZw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVP5CsZw.png&h=61d7589c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有乜問題<br />\n<br />\n驚失職？驚比人炒？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b4r2D6A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb4r2D6A.gif&h=0125c8ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你覺得佢做得長咩？<br />\n<br />\n為維持社會秩序？為公義？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AFkKSsJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAFkKSsJ.jpg&h=1b99a6fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(71林鄭出席回歸酒會，同日街頭)<br />\n你仲同意呢個政權係代表秩序同公義咩？<br />\n<br />\n為家庭？<br />\n宜家警嫂都上埋枱，為左自己嘅事業、呢個不公嘅政權，值得咩？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">諗唔明警察上前線為乜</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c52957e8142b741c818eca4d41ab5df3f5ffd2b5","tid":1505231,"uid":214036,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:20:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"232f45dbce275742234a199ac3255127d3c35aa9","tid":1505231,"uid":29899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:20:32.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 官逼民反，民不得不反<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dJNfyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dJNfyS</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br 